events.title: Study Group - Algorithms & Data Structures
events.description: Weekly study group for TUM Computer Science students preparing for the Algorithms and Data Structures exam. We'll work through practice problems and review key concepts.

events.title: Coffee & Code
events.description: Casual meetup for developers and computer science students. Bring your laptop and work on personal projects while meeting like-minded people.

events.title: Machine Learning Workshop
events.description: Introduction to PyTorch and neural networks. We'll build a simple image classifier together. Basic Python knowledge required.

events.title: Mathematics Tutoring Session
events.description: Group tutoring for Linear Algebra and Analysis. Open to all TUM engineering students.

events.title: International Students Welcome Party
events.description: Welcome party for new international students at LMU and TUM. Food, drinks, and great conversations guaranteed!

events.title: Business Case Competition Prep
events.description: Preparation session for the upcoming Munich Business Case Competition. Teams of 4-5 students will work on real business challenges.

events.title: Rock Climbing Session
events.description: Weekly climbing session for university students. All skill levels welcome. Equipment can be rented on-site.

events.title: Medical Students Study Circle
events.description: Study group for medical students preparing for anatomy exam. We'll use models and practice identification.

events.title: Photography Walk: Munich Architecture
events.description: Explore Munich's architectural diversity with fellow photography enthusiasts. Bring your camera (smartphone is fine too).

events.title: Robotics Project Demo Day
events.description: Students showcase their robotics projects. Open presentations followed by hands-on demonstrations.

events.title: Law Students Moot Court
events.description: Practice moot court session for law students. Case materials will be provided one week in advance.

events.title: Startup Pitch Practice
events.description: Practice your startup pitch in a friendly environment. Get feedback from fellow entrepreneurs and mentors.

events.title: Chemistry Lab Safety Workshop
events.description: Mandatory safety workshop for new chemistry students. Covers lab protocols, emergency procedures, and equipment handling.

events.title: Design Thinking Workshop
events.description: Learn design thinking methodology through hands-on exercises. Perfect for students from all disciplines.

events.title: Physics Colloquium: Quantum Computing
events.description: Guest lecture on recent advances in quantum computing hardware. Followed by Q&A and networking.
